msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#: content/darkroom/pixelpipe/the-pixelpipe-and-module-order.md
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "_Scene-referred_ modules are intended to process pixel values that are proportional to the amount of light collected by the camera at the scene. The dynamic range of an image in the scene-referred section of the pixelpipe is often larger than that of the display medium. \n"
