#. type: Plain text
#: content/lighttable/lighttable-modes/culling.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"zoom\n"
": In culling mode, you can zoom into images (up to 100%) by holding Ctrl while scrolling with the mouse wheel.\n"
": Pan within zoomed images with click+drag.\n"
