#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/rgb-levels.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Moving the black and white bars to match the left and right borders of the histogram will make the output image span the full available tonal range. This will increase the image's contrast. \n"
msgstr "Mover las barras en blanco y negro para que coincidan con los bordes izquierdo y derecho del histograma hará que la imagen de salida abarque todo el rango tonal disponible. Esto aumentará el contraste de la imagen. \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/rgb-levels.md
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "Moving the middle bar will modify the middle-gray tones. Move it to the left to make the image look brighter and move it to the right to make it darker. This is often referred to as changing the image's gamma.\n"
msgid "Moving the middle bar will modify the mid-tones. Move it to the left to make the image look brighter and move it to the right to make it darker. This is often referred to as changing the image's gamma.\n"
msgstr "Mover la barra del medio modificará los tonos de gris medio. Muévalo hacia la izquierda para que la imagen se vea más brillante y muévalo hacia la derecha para oscurecerla. Esto a menudo se denomina cambio de gamma de la imagen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/rgb-levels.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Three color pickers are available for sampling the black, white and gray points from the image. \n"
msgstr "Hay tres selectores de colores disponibles para muestrear los puntos negros, blancos y grises de la imagen. \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/rgb-levels.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"mode\n"
": The mode of operation. \"RGB, linked channels\" (default) provides a single levels tool which updates all channels, taking into account the selected color preservation method (see \"preserve colors\" below). \"RGB, independent channels\" provides separate levels controls for each of the R, G and B channels.\n"
msgstr ""
"modo\n"
": El modo de funcionamiento. \"RGB, canales vinculados\" (predeterminado) proporciona una herramienta de niveles únicos que actualiza todos los canales, teniendo en cuenta el método de conservación del color seleccionado (consulte \"conservar colores\" a continuación). \"RGB, canales independientes\" proporciona controles de niveles separados para cada uno de los canales R, G y B.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/rgb-levels.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"auto\n"
": Auto-adjust the black and white point and put the gray point exactly in the mean between them. Use the color picker to auto-adjust based on a selected region of the image.\n"
msgstr ""
