#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/color-balance-rgb.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "This is conceptually equivalent to the _lift_ from _lift/gamma/gain_, although implemented differently, and falls back to multiplying the masked pixels by a constant RGB value. It is applied using the _shadows_ mask.\n"
msgstr "Esto es conceptualmente equivalente al _realce_ de _realce/gamma/incremento_, aunque implementado de manera diferente, y recurre a la multiplicación de los píxeles enmascarados por un valor RGB constante. Se aplica mediante la máscara _sombras_.\n"

#. type: Title ###
