msgstr "![filmstrip](./filmstrip/filmstrip.png)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/filmstrip.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The filmstrip can be switched on and off using the shortcut Ctrl+F. The height of the filmstrip panel can be changed by clicking and dragging its top border.\n"
